edu.ucla.sspace.util
Interface Indexer<T>

All Superinterfaces:
Iterable<Map.Entry<T,Integer>>
All Known Implementing Classes:
HashIndexer, ObjectIndexer, TypedIsomorphicGraphIndexer
public interface Indexer<T>
extends Iterable<Map.Entry<T,Integer>>

A utility class for mapping a set of objects to unique indices. The indices returned by this class will always being at 0.

See Also:
Counter
